the day before your interview.

166
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,690
Who is the one that came up

167
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,920
with this birthday surprise idea?

168
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:38,740
Give me a moment.

169
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:40,220
