238
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:37,390
Who is it?

239
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,900
Yes.

240
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:40,730
It's

241
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:44,460
him.

242
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:50,240
